{"id": 2055, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X大众汽车】作为一枚低头族，你都遇到过什么人生困境？", "description": "低头两小时，按摩大半生。", "record_count": 15704, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171207181917o2RIGCLQDmHau0eB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-08T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 253440, "content": "被亲妈说有了颈纹显老以后不得不提早五年买颈霜才知道心疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076245}, {"id": 253696, "content": "只有装作在玩手机，才能找到一点存在感", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209971}, {"id": 253952, "content": "脖子病到什么程度不知道，正在量变到质变过程中！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137345}, {"id": 253441, "content": "沉浸在自己的世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182472}, {"id": 253442, "content": "这个跟大众汽车有什么关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122934}, {"id": 253700, "content": "在公共场所很少做低头族，只是开着音频暂时听力障碍而已~", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 262405, "content": "K\n\n\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847161}, {"id": 253445, "content": "很幸运不是低头族，自控能力还是很强的", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913697}, {"id": 253701, "content": "脸也变成了屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1170915}, {"id": 253703, "content": "真的不喜欢，眼睛疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853413}, {"id": 253449, "content": "现在已经习惯性低头了，跟别人说话都低头不看人脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208262}, {"id": 253450, "content": "坐车坐过站", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208286}, {"id": 253451, "content": "特别等人时候，不看手机感觉一阵尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010310}, {"id": 257803, "content": "看手机地图迷路了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726744}, {"id": 253452, "content": "不看手机仿佛不知道该干些什么，整个人失去了方向感", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208292}, {"id": 253455, "content": "抬头，几乎所有人都在低头\n低头，马路的杀手又不抬头", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208267}, {"id": 253456, "content": "越来越不会说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208317}, {"id": 253712, "content": "也没什么，就是25了还拿着2000块钱工资不让出去闯荡，父母总是说，房子车都是现成的钱也有，不需要你赚钱。可是我想证明的是我自己，不是你们。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210012}, {"id": 253713, "content": "手机建立的人与人的联系慢慢转型为人与人的频闭器。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678667}, {"id": 253461, "content": "大概是..日常瞎了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199384}, {"id": 253718, "content": "将这两者结合是来说，未免有点尴尬了吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1167223}, {"id": 253463, "content": "脖子疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208368}, {"id": 253464, "content": "好不容易想抬起头，发现大家都低着头，自己不知道该做什么好", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146804}, {"id": 253465, "content": "越尴尬越低头，瞅手机", "image": "img/option/option/20171209230700uYA9SXwjfdFJn7cD", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192050}, {"id": 253466, "content": "丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198188}, {"id": 253722, "content": "脖子疼的时候，抬头发现，这不是我想要的梦境。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210048}, {"id": 253467, "content": "这个年纪已经颈椎轻微骨质增生，沦落到去找盲人按摩…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670629}, {"id": 253468, "content": "并没有完全沉浸进去………", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106176}, {"id": 253471, "content": "最不喜欢边走路边玩手机，怕撞到什么?也不喜欢别人这样，在我们说话的时候。???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208445}, {"id": 253473, "content": "手机的影响是巨大的，但我们要把作用理清，不要被手机左右了生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208469}, {"id": 253729, "content": "低头是美女\n抬头是恐龙。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948126}, {"id": 253985, "content": "四层颈纹三层下巴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211778}, {"id": 253731, "content": "没有手机就没法出门了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210065}, {"id": 253476, "content": "不想谈恋爱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195392}, {"id": 253733, "content": "一个人尴尬所以低头族\n两个人不熟所以低头族\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210077}, {"id": 255269, "content": "看不清修行5000年的有缘人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217941}, {"id": 253478, "content": "我觉得自己没有很大的手机依赖症，但是在对面走过来很多人，而我只一个人时，我就会下意识看手机，刷两下，再有就是坐车的时候，真的不知道该如何处理视线，只能看手机看书睡觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208521}, {"id": 253479, "content": "觉得再也不可能出现电影里被人搭讪的桥段了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204768}, {"id": 259624, "content": "颈椎病。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599474}, {"id": 262697, "content": "没手机，不知道做什么。有手机也不知道做什么，但总是要手上拿着手机才安心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250455}, {"id": 262443, "content": "颈椎不舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242148}, {"id": 253739, "content": "盯着手机看，别人不会觉得奇怪。盯着一个地方看，别人大概觉得这个人脑袋有点问题吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210098}, {"id": 253485, "content": "缓解尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208578}, {"id": 256813, "content": "我现在就在走路边看来着(๑• . •๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078063}, {"id": 253486, "content": "不拿手机不知道该做些什么，大家都拿着手机，自己很尴尬的说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207915}, {"id": 253742, "content": "可能会错过最不该错过的人吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210109}, {"id": 259632, "content": "周末发现 突然放下手机发现今天一天嗓子没说过一句话 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218760}, {"id": 254770, "content": "逃避尴尬聚会 上N个闹钟假装电话不断有急事?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215792}, {"id": 259634, "content": "地铁上不断在我要到达的站摆动 不是往左过一站就是往右过一站", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218760}, {"id": 253491, "content": "到隔壁楼的蔬果超市买了鸡蛋回家，结果进楼道的时候因为看手机撞墙上碎了将近一半", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 395242}]}